
feat: add new feature
fix: fix bug
docs: update documentation
style: code style changes
refactor: code refactor
perf: performance improvement
test: add/update tests
chore: maintenance tasks
ci: CI/CD changes
Breaking change: add ! after type (e.g., feat!: breaking change)
Scope: optional, e.g., feat(blockchain): add new block
Example: feat(security): pin all GitHub Actions to SHAs
